{{$NEXT}}

0.04     2016-10-02

- Added a jobs configuration option.

- Made the generated test an author test, since it should pass on every
  commit.


0.03     2016-05-29

- Added a minimum_perl configuration option. If set, then the test will be
  skipped on Perl versions that don't meet this requirement. This is useful if
  you have tidyall plugins that require a certain version of Perl.


0.02     2016-04-24

- Added a verbose option and a TEST_TIDYALL_VERBOSE env var.


0.01     2015-01-11

- First release upon an unsuspecting world.
